                <h2>üåä Destination of the Month: Chesapeake Bay Islands</h2>
                <p>With fall colors in full display, the Chesapeake offers incredible cruising opportunities. Our top three picks for October:</p>
                
                <h3>1. Tilghman Island</h3>
                <p>A working waterman's village with authentic charm. Dock at Knapp's Narrows Marina and enjoy fresh crab cakes at the Bridge Restaurant overlooking the harbor.</p>
                
                <h3>2. St. Michaels</h3>
                <p>Upscale dining, boutique shopping, and the excellent Chesapeake Bay Maritime Museum. Town Dock Marina puts you in the heart of everything.</p>
                
                <h3>3. Solomons Island</h3>
                <p>Perfect for a weekend getaway with excellent facilities at Zahniser's Marina. Don't miss sunset cocktails at The Tiki Bar.</p>
                
                <p><strong>Navigation Note:</strong> Watch for crab pot markers in all these areas‚Äîthey're particularly dense in fall harvest season.</p>
